-- Climex to Hold Reverse Auction for Voluntary CO2 Offset Buyer
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r o   V i t e l l i
-- 2012-10-18T13:21:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-18/climex-to-hold-reverse-auction-for-voluntary-co2-offset-buyer.html
Climex BV, the Amsterdam-based
auction platform for emissions permits and offsets, will host a
reverse auction of Verified Emission Reductions on Nov. 9.  The buyer is seeking to purchase 100,000 offsets from wind
power, biomass or bioenergy projects certified by the  Gold
Standard , Climex said in an e-mailed statement today. The
auction will start with a maximum price of 5.50 euros ($7.21) a
metric ton.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alessandro Vitelli in London at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
